= Dragon Warrior IV (NES) Shop List =

This page documents all shops in '''Dragon Warrior IV''' (NES, US version), organized by chapter and location.

== Overview ==

Dragon Warrior IV features shops in towns throughout the five chapters. Item availability varies by location and story progression. Shop data is stored in Bank $06.

